<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.8130050>
    dc:description "FIGURES 186–195. (186)Heterotrioza chenopodii, male terminalia, lateral view.(187)Lauritrioza laurisilvae, male terminalia, lateral view. (188–195) Percyella spp.; (188) head, dorsal view (P. benahorita); (189) antenna (P. guanche); (190) antenna, showing rhinaria (P. guanche); (191) proboscis (P. gomerita); (192) metacoxa (P. gomerita); (193) forewing (P. gomerita); (194) forewing (P. guanche); (195) hindwing (P. gomerita)." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/8130050/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.8130062>
    dc:description "FIGURES 212–218. Fifth-instar immature; (212–214) Lauritrioza laurisilvae: (212) habitus, right half; (213) marginal sectasetae and simple setae on forewing pad; (214) marginal sectasetae and simple setae on caudal plate. (215–218) Percyella species: (215) habitus, right half; (216) modified tarsal arolium and claws, lateral view; (217) modified tarsal arolium and claws, dorsal view; (218) circumanal rings and anus." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/8130062/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.8130085>
    dc:description "FIGURES 269–280. (269–271) Lauritrioza laurisilvae: (269, 270) adult, habitus; (269) lateral view; (270) dorsal view; (271) immature. (272, 273) Percyella canari: adult, habitus; (272) lateral view; (273) dorsal view. (274–276) Percyella gomerita, adult, habitus, dorsal view. (277–280) Percyella guanche: (277) Acari attached to the abdomen; (278) adult, habitus, dorsal view; (279, 280) immature. Photographs 269 and 270 by Alfonso Peña Darias." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/8130085/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

